{"tid":1559272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"零風險輕鬆分辨藍黃店鋪大法和理非同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T09:26:44.000Z","uid":91659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8c7fe5edf0c742d38b8a7026a2b8a581ff16072","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲都分唔到邊間店舖係咩立場，萬一入左間藍店食野真係背脊骨落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如我地從自己嘅社區做起，用一個簡單嘅符號貼喺已 fact check 立場嘅舖頭度，咁搵野食買野就容易得多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n具體操作：<br />\n<br />\n1. 決定一個冇冒犯性嘅標記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（例如黃色同藍色 memo 紙，淨色貼紙.etc）<br />\n<br />\n2. 決定用作辨認嘅位置 （例如每間鋪頭嘅門口右下角）<br />\n<br />\n3. Fact check 確認店舖是否推薦光顧<br />\n<br />\n4. 輕輕將標記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼上，大功告成。<br />\n<br />\n以後每去一間店鋪前，都順手望一下門口右下角有冇標記：藍貼紙就唔好入，黃貼紙就買買買，唔洗下下上網 check<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n<br />\n1. 標記不宜過大，以免被太多人發現清除<br />\n<br />\n2. 不宜用藍黃貼紙等意識明顯嘅標記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可用其他顏色圖案，大家 get 到就得<br />\n<br />\n3. 確認左先好貼，免殺錯無辜<br />\n<br />\n4. 要張貼在不會被貨物遮住嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要大家養成順手望一眼嘅小習慣，就可以為香港本地出一分力，而且完全合法零風險！零風險！零風險！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nforward 去各區 tg 實踐下～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a010f2217344a74f15f798a5a757bba9d33c651","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"04eb851403fe8227b946cf81181f029ffbd7469b","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"3dae95afedb90a4666fca91e46635f9d02d949af","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3330885c7e92097a66508ba4c8941f8f903465d4","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9f392709c56e71c31ed15017745fc0da1834ea3c","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d29af7a708a1380f6f895881d47e3a3f4f23a1f1","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:21.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d5dafd63ec66a3a7224899acd0eb39baea20d5e4","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"378b950054980e29492e7d89882fee45cde916b5","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"16521b9d84362f0cff1b358c9be3288c043d29a8","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c1d3d2615166abc56e21d9805a44751aef60fe77","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fde0eb26249ba0f8551988973c14b5df3eef200b","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:37:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2d1e0f1e054afbc950c2ced0a8ed7c46873c087f","tid":1559272,"uid":20231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"人地會清架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d84e74362cfaef89195ff01aa2c28d3d6340ee7","tid":1559272,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"成功十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190bd1373d75734d7f74ae190a69c18641557942","tid":1559272,"uid":134751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0